🍽️ Restaurant Management API
Backend REST API built with Golang, Gin, GORM, MySQL & JWT Authentication
<p align="left"> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.24-00ADD8?style=for-the-badge&logo=go&logoColor=white" alt="Go"/> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Gin-Web_Framework-00C7B7?style=for-the-badge" alt="Gin"/> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GORM-ORM-blue?style=for-the-badge" alt="GORM"/> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/MySQL-Database-orange?style=for-the-badge&logo=mysql&logoColor=white" alt="MySQL"/> <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/JWT-Authentication-red?style=for-the-badge" alt="JWT"/> </p>
📖 Overview

Restaurant Management API is a backend application developed using Golang, Gin, GORM, and MySQL.

The project provides REST APIs for managing restaurant operations including:

👤 User Management
🍔 Food Management
📋 Menu Management
🪑 Table Management
🛒 Order Management
📦 Order Item Management
🧾 Invoice Management
🔐 JWT Authentication
🚀 Features
👤 User Module
Register User
Login User
Update User
Delete User
🍔 Food Module
Add Food
Update Food
Delete Food
📋 Menu Module
Create Menu
Update Menu
Delete Menu
🪑 Table Module
Create Table
Update Table
Delete Table
🛒 Order Module
Create Order
Update Order
Delete Order
📦 Order Item Module
Add Order Item
Update Order Item
Delete Order Item
🧾 Invoice Module
Generate Invoice
View Invoice
🔐 Security
JWT Authentication
Protected Routes
Middleware
