⚙️ Installation
Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/restaurant-management-api.git
Go to Project
cd restaurant-management-api
Install Dependencies
go mod tidy
Run Application
go run main.go

The application will run on:

http://localhost:8080
🔐 Authentication

All protected APIs require:

Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
